      <guid>https://fbez.github.io/workshop-esp-idf/workshops/esp-idf-advanced/lecture-3/</guid>
      <description>In this article, we cover size analysis and core dumps. You’ll learn what they do, why they matter, and how to use them to build more efficient and reliable applications.</description>
      
    </item>
    
